cs.CL, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing and structured query generation, which are core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). It also involves database schema and query optimization, which are relevant to database systems (cs.DB). The paper proposes a novel approach using GAN-based data augmentation, which falls under the category of generative models and deep learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on benchmark datasets, which is a common practice in information retrieval (cs.IR).
